sql: CREATE TABLE bronze.games(gameId BIGINT, season BIGINT, "week" BIGINT, gameDate DATE, gameTimeEastern TIME, homeTeamAbbr VARCHAR, visitorTeamAbbr VARCHAR, homeFinalScore BIGINT, visitorFinalScore BIGINT);
